                <Icon BackgroundTint="#000000" IconRect="126,84,168,126" IconResource="images/icons/icon_ms1.dds" IconStyle="/IconStyles.button" Location="23,43" MouseOverColor="#FFFF00" Name="Icon" PackLocation="left,top" ScrollExtent="42,42" Size="42,42" />
                <Text AbsorbsInput="false" Font="/TextStyles.Chat.ChatStyle" Location="76,40" Name="AboutText" ScrollExtent="490,320" Size="490,105">:b7b5c6e0385d9677:A guild is a group of characters who choose to band together. Guilds provide their members with several benefits such as a shared chat channel and a guild bank. At level 15 your guild will also gain heraldry to display on the members&apos; cloaks. Guilds can gain levels just like characters, allowing access to larger banks and reward items from city merchants.</Text>
                <Page Location="0,147" Name="InfoPage" ScrollExtent="580,190" Size="580,190">
                    <Icon BackgroundTint="#000000" IconRect="42,0,84,42" IconResource="images/icons/icon_ms1.dds" IconStyle="/IconStyles.button" Location="23,36" MouseOverColor="#FFFF00" Name="Icon" PackLocation="left,top" ScrollExtent="42,42" Size="42,42" />
                    <Text AbsorbsInput="false" Font="/TextStyles.VeryLarge.VeryLargeStyle" Location="16,0" Margin="5,5,5,5" Name="Header" PackSize="a" ScrollExtent="550,33" Size="550,30" TextColor="#F0E0B0">:b7b5c6e026b2dac3:How Do I Create a New Guild?</Text>
                    <Text AbsorbsInput="false" Font="/TextStyles.Chat.ChatStyle" Location="76,33" Name="InfoText" ScrollExtent="490,256" Size="490,105">:b7b5c6e0c9dc13ce:To create a guild, you must be the leader of a group of 6 characters. None of the characters in the group can already be in a guild. When the new guild is created the group leader will become the guild leader and the five other group members will become recruits in the guild.</Text>
                    <Text AbsorbsInput="false" BackgroundOpacity="0.275" Color="#FF0000" Font="/TextStyles.Chat.ChatStyle" Location="76,141" Name="Errors" PackLocation=",fff" ScrollExtent="490,48" Size="490,48">:b7b5c6e01e17f5ef:Error 1 Error 2 Error 3</Text>
