                    <Text AbsorbsInput="false" Font="/TextStyles.Chat.ChatStyle" Location="76,33" Name="CreateText" ScrollExtent="490,224" Size="490,90">:b7b5c6e0a68789b8:You can create a guild now. All the members of your group will automatically join the new guild as recruits and you will join as guild leader. The price to create a guild is 60s, which you will pay. Enter your desired guild name:</Text>
